{"id":"seno-04m","title":"SNOMED Validation v2: Validate dotbase codebook codes","description":"Validate all SNOMED codes from dotbase codebook against Snowstorm.\n\n**Source:** /Users/thome/gt/senologie/20260110_dotbase_codebook.xlsx\n- Column L ('Code (for choice)'): 2,873 entries\n- Column N ('Codesystem (SNOMED)'): 3,093 entries  \n- **678 unique SNOMED codes** to validate\n\n**Process:**\n1. Extract SNOMED codes from columns L and N (numeric 6-18 digit codes)\n2. Query Snowstorm for each code\n3. Get: validity, FSN, German designation, synonyms (DE+EN)\n4. Flag deprecated/replaced codes\n\n**Output:** JSON with structure:\n```json\n{\n  \"DGS_Term\": \"\u003cfrom Choice column\u003e\",\n  \"DGS_Code\": \"\u003cSNOMED code\u003e\",\n  \"status\": \"valid|deprecated|replaced|not_found\",\n  \"currentCode\": \"...\",\n  \"germanDesignation\": \"...\",\n  \"englishFSN\": \"...\",\n  \"synonyms_de\": [],\n  \"synonyms_en\": []\n}\n```\n\n**Note:** Previous attempt (seno-1p3) only validated 29 codes from FSH files - this task covers the full 678 codes.","status":"hooked","priority":1,"issue_type":"task","assignee":"senologie/polecats/furiosa","created_at":"2026-01-18T14:13:12.947233+01:00","created_by":"mayor","updated_at":"2026-01-18T14:13:52.557746+01:00"}
