{"id":"seno-1p3","title":"SNOMED Validation: Validate and document all SNOMED mappings","description":"Validate all DGS Senologie SNOMED codes against local Snowstorm server (latest German Edition).\n\n**Background:**\n- German terms were mapped to SNOMED by clinician ~2 years ago\n- Methodology not clean, terms may have changed\n- Some response options may not have had SNOMED codes then but do now\n\n**Source:** Original Excel (Senologie_Datensatz_20250606.xlsx) - 9 sheets, 2748 fields\n\n**Deliverable:** JSON feedback document for clinician review before profiling.\n\n**JSON Structure:**\n```json\n{\n  \"validationDate\": \"2026-01-18\",\n  \"snomedVersion\": \"\u003cfrom snowstorm\u003e\",\n  \"mappings\": [\n    {\n      \"DGS_Term\": \"Mammakarzinom\",\n      \"DGS_Code\": \"254837009\",\n      \"status\": \"valid|deprecated|replaced|not_found|new_mapping\",\n      \"currentCode\": \"...\",\n      \"germanDesignation\": \"...\",\n      \"englishFSN\": \"...\",\n      \"synonyms_de\": [],\n      \"synonyms_en\": [],\n      \"notes\": \"...\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```","status":"closed","priority":1,"issue_type":"epic","assignee":"senologie/polecats/furiosa","created_at":"2026-01-18T13:46:32.86308+01:00","created_by":"mayor","updated_at":"2026-01-18T13:54:55.848348+01:00","closed_at":"2026-01-18T13:54:55.848348+01:00","close_reason":"Closed"}
